text: Hamburger Straße is a rapid transit station located in the Hamburg district of Barmbek-Süd, Germany. The elevated station was opened in 1912 and is served by Hamburg U-Bahn line U3. == Service == === Trains === Hamburger Straße is served by Hamburg U-Bahn line U3; departures are every 5 minutes. == See also == * List of Hamburg U-Bahn stations ==References== == External links == * Line and route network plans at hvv.de Category:Hamburg U-Bahn stations in Hamburg Category:Buildings and structures in Hamburg-Nord Hamburg HamburgerStr Hamburg HamburgerStr
